    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Social Media Manager"
      subtitle="2024 at TradeWithLumide, Lagos, Nigeria"
    >
      Develop and execute socia media ad strategies. Manage ad campaigns and track performance. Creating engaging content that drives traffic. Collaborated with the marketing team for alignment. Created a buyer persona for the brand.
