    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Entry"
      subtitle="From Nov 2021 to Apr 2022 at Lagos Writers, Lagos, Nigeria"
    >
      Accurately recorded and managed data,ensuring that all informations are entered correctly and efficiently. Ensured data integrity and consistency through regular checks and updates.
    </TimeLineElement>
