      title="Data Entry"
      subtitle="From Feb 2021 to Jul 2021 at The Memo Communication, Lagos, Nigeria"
    Accurately transferring data from paper format into database system. Performs regular backups in ensuring data preservation. Updating existing data. Ensuring the safety of all clients personal information.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

